(v_i)_{i=1}^n
(u_i)_{i=1}^n
\sum_{s\in\{0,1\}^{n}} \exp\left(\sum_{i=1}^{n}\sum_{i=1}^{n}u_{i}v_{j}s_{i}s_{j}\right) \\ = \sum_{s\in\{0,1\}^{n}} \exp\left(\sum_{i=1}^{n}u_{i}s_{i}\sum_{j=1}^{n}v_{j}s_{j}\right) \\ = \sum_{s\in\{0,1\}^{n}}\exp\left(\sum_{i=1}^{n}t_{i}s_{i}\right)
t_{i} = \displaystyle u_{i}\left(\sum_{j=1}^{n}v_{j}s_{j}\right)
\mathcal{M} = \{0,1\}^{n}
M=n
\mu = s
